    {
      "id": "740894d9-22df-4613-ab68-f2dbad1655b7",
      "agentId": "claude",
      "name": "claude-heartbeat",
      "enabled": true,
      "createdAtMs": 1772931027927,
      "updatedAtMs": 1774860712925,
      "schedule": {
        "kind": "every",
        "everyMs": 1800000,
        "anchorMs": 1772931027927
      },
      "sessionTarget": "isolated",
      "wakeMode": "now",
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "# HEARTBEAT.md — Claude\n\n## Loop\n\nWhen triggered, follow this loop until there is nothing left to do:\n\n1. **Read `TODO.md`** — find the first task with status `[ ]`\n2. **Do it** — reason through it, build it, fix it, decide it\n3. **Test it** — verify the output is correct and complete\n4. **Log it** — append a one-line entry to `PROGRESS-LOG.md`: `[timestamp] task — result`\n5. **Update `TODO.md`** — mark done `[x]`, spawn follow-up tasks `[ ]` if any\n6. **Keep going** — return to step 1. Only stop when `TODO.md` has no `[ ]` items.\n\nIf `TODO.md` is empty, scan for blocked work across the team:\n- Check `site/notes.md` for blockers or questions from other agents\n- Check `site/qa/bugs.md` for critical/high severity bugs unaddressed\n- Check if any agent workspaces have stalled (no progress log entries in 30+ min)\n\nIf work is found, add it to `TODO.md` and begin the loop. If nothing is found, reply `HEARTBEAT_OK`."
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "none"
      },
